### Make credits

```go{ id: 3 }
Show(Transaction(aliceAddr).
    WithSigner(aliceAddr).
    AddCredits(aliceAddr, 10).
        Oracle(5).
    Initiate(alice).
    Submit().
    Wait())
Show(Get(aliceAddr))
```

