### Send tokens

```go{ id: 4 }
bob, charlie := GenerateKey("bob"), GenerateKey("charlie")
bobAddr, charlieAddr := LiteAddress(bob, ACME), LiteAddress(charlie, ACME)

Show(Transaction(aliceAddr).
    WithSigner(aliceAddr).
    SendTokens().
        To(bobAddr, 68).
        AndTo(charlieAddr, 42).
    Initiate(alice).
    Submit().
    Wait())
Show(Get(aliceAddr))
Show(Get(bobAddr))
Show(Get(charlieAddr))
```

